lyrics:
[verse]
In the streets of Mumbai, where love was found
Two souls collided on this merry ground
Their hearts intertwined, a sweet melody
A Hindi teenage love song, a symphony

[chorus]
Oh, tu hai meri, main hoon tera
Pyar ki dhun, hum dono ka savera
Jeevan saathi, dil ki nishaani
Hindi pyaar ka geet, gubbare ki kahani
